title: SDOG Crosses Above Key Moving Average Level - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of the SDOG ETF (Symbol: SDOG) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $42.63, changing hands as high as $42.89 per share. SDOG shares are currently trading up about 1.7% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of SDOG shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, SDOG's low point in its 52 week range is $36.9202 per share, with $46.8799 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $42.83.
